snippet.title: Best VGM 2437 - YU-NO : A Girl Who Chants Love at the Bound of this World (PC-98) - Fate
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC-98
YU-NO: A Girl Who Chants Love at the Bound of this World (1996)
Fate
Ryu Umemoto
